Class SuperPeer

  • java.lang.Object
    • jade.core.Agent

          • agents.SuperPeer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    jade.core.TimerListener, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, P2PVocabulary

    public class SuperPeer
extends Peer
    A Super Peer has more bandwidth, and thus more responsibilities in the network. In addition to the properties of all Peers, Super Peers maintain an extra list of ordinary peer IDs and their list of shared files.
